    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the S65 V8 with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This chassis is in museum-grade condition, featuring a documented rod bearing service and a recent throttle actuator overhaul to mitigate common platform failure points. The undercarriage is free of oxidation, and the bushings remain compliant yet firm, preserving the original kinematic integrity of the multi-link rear suspension. With flawless paint meter readings and an interior devoid of typical UV degradation or bolster compression, this example satisfies the most discerning mechanical scrutiny.",
